author: Wendy Lee
title: YouTube launches video subscription service
text:
Photo: Danny Moloshok, Associated Press Robert Kyncl, YouTube chief business officer, outlines the new subscription service, called YouTube Red, in Los Angeles. Robert Kyncl, YouTube chief business officer, outlines the new...
YouTube announced a monthly subscription service Wednesday that starts at $10, allowing users to play videos without ads, offline and in the background while using other apps.
